reviews.review_text:
amazing show and recording This was one of my favorite tapes about 25 years ago.  Superior versions of Rooster, Deep Elum, LLRain and Deal (and I rarely enjoy Rooster or LLR).  Quite possibly the best-ever To Lay Me Down, too.

Impeccable recording.  Thanks Bob and Charlie!
lakeland 80' solid first set with nice song selection.jerry is in nice form with some sweet jams.phil is nice in the mix,gr8 sound.i would recommend this one.
